From 5e8382a220c7ed469a1049c41642dda2a7742b7b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Benjamin A. Beasley" <code@musicinmybrain.net>
Date: Tue, 26 Mar 2024 13:25:24 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Update tests for latest hatchling.

Based on:
https://github.com/repo-helper/hatch-requirements-txt/commit/1aa21b86db3503ed46683fa7af748d7aa1e853e1

Cherry-picked to 0.4.1; changes to files in .github/ managed by
repo_helper omitted.
---
 repo_helper.yml      | 41 ++++++++++++++-------
 tests/test_errors.py | 53 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 tox.ini              | 85 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--------------
 3 files changed, 141 insertions(+), 38 deletions(-)

